Sprint 2 - Reflection Log

What went well:
- Project management comptency despite goals not being achieved.

What went wrong and why:

- The sprint goals were not achieved due to a misunderstanding of the sprint cadence — I mistakenly assumed the sprint review occurred at the end rather than mid-sprint. As a result, I misallocated time and shifted focus to clearing previously delayed tasks, updating Trello to reflect these changes.

How we can improve:

- Treat the Gantt chart as a strict timeline rather than a loose guide, ensuring it is regularly updated and re-aligned with sprint meetings and deliverables.
